Linux instructions:

Install ruby, rubygem. Run in terminal
sudo gem install nokogiri
sudo gem install parseconfig
sudo gem install unicode_utils

run in terminal ./run_listener.sh

**********************************

Windows instructions:

Install ruby (e.g. from http://rubyinstaller.org)

Install needed gems by running `cmd` and executing following commands:
gem install nokogiri
gem install parseconfig
gem install unicode_utils

Install growl notifications system (e.g. from http://growl.info)

open scripts folder in windows command line promt
run in cmd promt 'run_listener.cmd'
(windows users can also run `chcp 65001` in cmd promt in order to change code page to 65001 - unicode)

